HEADWORD: Excreate
<hw>Ex"cre*ate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>excreare</ets>, <ets>exsreare</ets>; <ets>ex</ets> out +
<ets>screare</ets> to hawk.]</ety> <def>To spit out; to discharge from
the throat by hawking and spitting.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Cockeram.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

